          "id": 1,
          "question": "<p><a name=\"3411\"></a><div itemprop=\"text\">\n<p>The number of states required by a Finite State Machine,to simulate the behavior of a computer with a memory capable of storing 'm' words, each of length 'n' bits is?</p>\n\n\n</div><br><br><b>ISRO CSE 2014 | Question: 2</b></p>",
          "type": "single",
          "options": [
            "<p>\\( m \\times 2^n \\)</p>",
            "<p>\\( 2^{m+n} \\)</p>",
            "<p>\\( 2^{mn} \\)</p>",
            "<p>\\( m+n \\)</p>"
          ],
          "correct_answer": "<p>\\( 2^{mn} \\)</p>",
